ted code from [the init part of WebGLRenderer](https:\/\/github.com\/spite\/three.js\/blob\/615e25b578f8f3ec0fdcab0045996956143d6dba\/src\/renderers\/WebGLRenderer.js#L252).\r\n\r\nIdea: All the `if` could be replaced by a `Map` in `.convert()`.\r\n\r\nQuestion: Should `WebGLUtils` replace all `threeParamToGL` calls in the code?","created_at":"2017-07-27T22:52:29.000Z","html_url":"https:\/\/github.com\/mrdoob\/three.js\/pull\/11846#issuecomment-318508719","id":318508719,"issue_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/repos\/mrdoob\/three.js\/issues\/11846","node_id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDMxODUwODcxOQ==","updated_at":"2017-07-27T22:52:29.000Z","url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/repos\/mrdoob\/three.js\/issues\/comments\/318508719","user":{"following_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/spite\/following{\/other_user}","events_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/spite\/events{\/privacy}","avatar_url":"https:\/\/avatars3.githubusercontent.com\/u\/731885?v=4","url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/spite","gists_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/spite\/gists{\/gist_id}","html_url":"https:\/\/github.com\/spite","subscriptions_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/spite\/subscriptions","node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjczMTg4NQ==","repos_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/spite\/repos","received_events_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/spite\/received_events","gravatar_id":"","starred_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/spite\/starred{\/owner}{\/repo}","site_admin":false,"login":"spite","type":"User","id":731885,"followers_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/spite\/followers","organizations_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/spite\/orgs"}},{"index":4,"author_association":"OWNER","body":"> I'm not entirely happy with [this part](https:\/\/github.com\/spite\/three.js\/blob\/615e25b578f8f3ec0fdcab0045996956143d6dba\/src\/extras\/WebGLUtils.js#L11), because it's repeated code from [the init part of WebGLRenderer](https:\/\/github.com\/spite\/three.js\/blob\/615e25b578f8f3ec0fdcab0045996956143d6dba\/src\/renderers\/WebGLRenderer.js#L252).\r\n\r\nYeah, that's a bit too aggressive. I think I would do this:\r\n\r\n```js\r\nfunction WebGLUtils( gl, extensions ) {\r\n\r\n    function convert() {}\r\n    return { convert: convert }\r\n\r\n}\r\n\r\nexport { WebGLUtils }\r\n```\r\n\r\nThen in `WebGLRenderer`:\r\n\r\n```js\r\nutils = new WebGLUtils( _gl, extensions );\r\n```\r\n\r\n```js\r\nutils.convert( foo );\r\n```\r\n\r\nThen, in `UpdatableTexture` you could do this:\r\n\r\n```js\r\nvar utils = new THREE.WebGLUtils( renderer.context, renderer.extensions );\r\n```\r\n\r\n> Question: Should `WebGLUtils` replace all `threeParamToGL` calls in the code?\r\n\r\nYep!","created_at":"2017-07-28T03:05:43.000Z","html_url":"https:\/\/github.com\/mrdoob\/three.js\/pull\/11846#issuecomment-318544205","id":318544205,"issue_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/repos\/mrdoob\/three.js\/issues\/11846","node_id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDMxODU0NDIwNQ==","updated_at":"2017-07-28T03:05:43.000Z","url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/repos\/mrdoob\/three.js\/issues\/comments\/318544205","user":{"following_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/mrdoob\/following{\/other_user}","events_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/mrdoob\/events{\/privacy}","avatar_url":"https:\/\/avatars0.githubusercontent.com\/u\/97088?v=4","url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/mrdoob","gists_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/mrdoob\/gists{\/gist_id}","html_url":"https:\/\/github.com\/mrdoob","subscriptions_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/mrdoob\/subscriptions","node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjk3MDg4","repos_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/mrdoob\/repos","received_events_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/mrdoob\/received_events","gravatar_id":"","starred_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/mrdoob\/starred{\/owner}{\/repo}","site_admin":false,"login":"mrdoob","type":"User","id":97088,"followers_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/mrdoob\/followers","organizations_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/mrdoob\/orgs"}},{"index":5,"author_association":"CONTRIBUTOR","body":"Much better with this design. I've updated `WebGLUtils` and replaced all calls to `threeParamToGL`. \r\n\r\n`WebGLTextures` and `WebGLState` had a reference to `threeParamToGL` in its constructor, I've replaced it with a reference to the renderer's `utils` object. But since they also get a reference to `gl` and `extensions`, may be they could create their own `WebGLUtils` instance. I don't think it makes a big difference one way or the other.","created_at":"2017-07-28T12:08:32.000Z","html_url":"https:\/\/github.com\/mrdoob\/three.js\/pull\/11846#issuecomment-318635558","id":318635558,"issue_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/repos\/mrdoob\/three.js\/issues\/11846","node_id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDMxODYzNTU1OA==","updated_at":"2017-07-28T12:08:32.000Z","url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/repos\/mrdoob\/three.js\/issues\/comments\/318635558","user":{"following_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/spite\/following{\/other_user}","events_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/spite\/events{\/privacy}","avatar_url":"https:\/\/avatars3.githubusercontent.com\/u\/731885?v=4","url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/spite","gists_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/spite\/gists{\/gist_id}","html_url":"https:\/\/github.com\/spite","subscriptions_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/spite\/subscriptions","node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjczMTg4NQ==","repos_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/spite\/repos","received_events_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/spite\/received_events","gravatar_id":"","starred_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/spite\/starred{\/owner}{\/repo}","site_admin":false,"login":"spite","type":"User","id":731885,"followers_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/spite\/followers","organizations_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/spite\/orgs"}},{"index":6,"author_association":"OWNER","body":"Beautiful!","created_at":"2017-07-28T19:38:20.000Z","html_url":"https:\